snippet.title: "What is Circuits and Shields?" in 2 minutes!
snippet.description:
Join the community: https://discord.gg/circuitsandshields

$750 Prize pool tournament coming up on June 19th - 20th! Come compete!
http://circuitsandshields.com/alphakickoffoverview

Play the game: http://circuitsandshields.com/alpha

The next generation of MOBA, Circuits and Shields features dynamic gameplay, streamlined systems, and thrilling game modes to create a modernized gaming experience. 

Circuits ditches the age old “Farm 10 minutes, fight 10 seconds” of classic MOBAs and introduces action-packed, objective-based arenas where you’ll always have a chance to make your mark through mechanical outplays OR precise team strategy.

Twitch: https://twitch.tv/circuitsandshields
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CircuitsGame
Instagram: http://instagram.com/circuitsandshields
Website: https://circuitsandshields.com
